  description: 'Increases Ability Power by 30. Grants "Eternal Scholar": Every 5
    seconds during combat, the wearer gains an additional 30 Ability Power. This
    effect stacks until the end of the battle. A heavy, leather-bound book with silver-edged
    pages that shimmer with arcane residue; it absorbs the ambient energy of the
    battlefield, translating the chaos of combat into a focused, unstoppable surge
    of magical power.'
